<h3 class="date"><a href="/2008/jun/01/">&#x27a0;</a> June 1, 2008</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="denyhosts" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://denyhosts.sourceforge.net/">DenyHosts</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Excellent Unix tool which watches for attacks on ssh and blocks malicious hosts from connecting.  I&#8217;ve only just found that it has a &#8220;synchronization&#8221; mode which shares the knowledge of evil hosts.  Installed on all my servers.</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
