        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.truecrypt.org/">TrueCrypt - Free Open-Source On-The-Fly Disk Encryption Software</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>The excellent TrueCrypt now runs on OS X, as well as Windows and Linux.  I&#8217;ll definitely be shunting some of my files onto an encrypted thumbdrive later.</p>

