<h3 class="date"><a href="/2007/may/03/">&#x27a0;</a> May 3, 2007</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="ext3cow" >

        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.ext3cow.com/">ext3cow</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>&#8220;Ext3cow is an open-source, versioning file system based on ext3.  It provides a time-shifting interface that allows a real-time and continuous view of the past.  This allows users to access their file system as it appeared at any point in time.&#8221;</p>

        <div class="row-fluid">
            <div class="span10">
                
